OL,3,CMan, 38, jailed for eight years after
OL,4,Csex offences against young girl
OL,6,FA 38-year-old man has been sentenced
OL,7,Fto eight years in prison for sexual
OL,8,Foffences against a young girl.
OL,10,FDavide Romano was found guilty of two
OL,11,Fcounts of sexual touching of a young
OL,12,Fchild and one count of causing a
OL,13,Fsexual act with a young child.
OL,15,FIn the four-day trial at Jersey's
OL,16,FRoyal Court in February, the jury
OL,17,Fheard how Romano made the child play
OL,18,Fwhat was called a 'blindfold game' and
OL,19,Fhow he made her touch him.
