OL,3,CMan, 38, jailed for eight years after
OL,4,Csex offences against young girl
OL,6,FAt the sentencing hearing on Thursday
OL,7,F24 April, Crown Advocate Lauren Hallam
OL,8,Fmade the case for a nine-year prison
OL,9,Fsentence.
OL,11,FRomano's counsel, Advocate Paul
OL,12,FNicholls, however, argued that such a
OL,13,Fsentence would be excessive and "so
OL,14,Fwrong that it frankly beggars belief".
