OL,3,CMan, 38, jailed for eight years after
OL,4,Csex offences against young girl
OL,6,FFollowing the verdict that Romano
OL,7,Fwould be jailed for eight years,
OL,8,FDetective Constable Jenny Docherty
OL,9,Ffrom the States of Jersey Police,
OL,10,Fsaid: "The victim has been clear and
OL,11,Fconsistent throughout, and I commend
OL,12,Fher for her bravery in reporting the
OL,13,Fcrime and giving evidence in court.
OL,15,F"Romano took advantage of age and
OL,16,Ftrust in order to sexually offend
OL,17,Fagainst the young victim in this case,
OL,18,Fthe attack was opportunistic and
OL,19,Fserious.
